&lt;h1 id="the-aging-entrepreneur"&gt;The Aging Entrepreneur&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Aug 8 2007&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Can older people be great entrepreneurs?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Marc Andreesen has a &lt;a href="http://blog.pmarca.com/2007/08/the-age-of-the-.html"&gt;great post&lt;/a&gt; on this age-old question. In part I, he&amp;rsquo;s digging through the data. Some of his observations are powerful and worth summarizing:&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>After the Ladder</title><link>https://linguista.cn/paul_graham/essays_en/ladder/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://linguista.cn/paul_graham/essays_en/ladder/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;→ &lt;a href="https://linguista.cn/paul_graham/essays_zh/ladder/"&gt;中文版本&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
